# Keep the build context tiny and avoid leaking junk into images
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.github
**/.idea
**/.vscode
**/.DS_Store
**/*.iml
**/target
**/build
**/out
**/node_modules
**/.terraform
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.*
**/.terragrunt-cache
**/*.tfvars
**/*.tfvars.json

# never let secrets reach the build context
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/*.crt
**/id_rsa*
**/id_ed25519*
**/credentials
**/aws-credentials
**/.aws

# docs and CI configs are not needed inside the image
README.md
RUNBOOK.md
COSTS.md
CHAOS.md
SECURITY.md
docs/
infra/
scripts/
evidence/
Makefile
